    Append test2 to results
    
    Note: Test resource cleanup during unload
    Let test3 be run_test("Resource Cleanup on Unload", test_resource_cleanup_on_unload)
    Append test3 to results
    
    Note: Test unloading non-existent plugin
    Let test4 be run_test("Unload Non-existent Plugin", test_unload_nonexistent_plugin)
    Append test4 to results
    
